    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document offers guidance for developing privacy considerations for inclusion in protocol specifications.  It aims to make designers, implementers, and users of Internet protocols aware of privacy-related design choices.  It suggests that whether any individual RFC warrants a specific privacy considerations section will depend on the document's content.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
